# skip-rule: kct-toolbar
#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the very top of the game window there are located the menubar and the "
"toolbar. In the center of the screen there is a large square area filled "
"with marbles called the game board. On the right hand side there located a "
"bar showing the next three marbles to be dropped onto the field (unless "
"<guimenuitem>Show Next</guimenuitem> feature is disabled). Below the playing "
"field there is the status bar."
msgstr ""
"A la part superior de la finestra de joc es troben les barres de menús i la "
"d'eines. Al centre de la pantalla hi ha una gran àrea quadrada plena de "
"bales anomenada el tauler de joc. A la part dreta, s'ubica una barra que "
"mostra les 3 bales següents que es deixaran caure al camp (a menys que "
"estigui inhabilitada la característica <guimenuitem>Mostra les següents</"
"guimenuitem>). A sota del camp hi ha la barra d'estat."

